			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	Castle Hotel.  Good morning.
<b>B:</b>	Good morning.  This is Andy Peterson.  I have a reservation for tonight, but I <blank word="will be" alt="'ll be" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>be</i>) very late.
<b>A:</b>	What time <blank word="will" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="arrive" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>arrive</i>)?
<b>B:</b>	I <blank word="will be" alt="'ll be" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>be</i>) at the hotel around 11:00 P.M.
<b>A:</b>	How long <blank word="will" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="stay" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>stay</i>)?
<b>B:</b>	Only one night.  I have a 9:00 A.M. flight to New York, so I <blank word="will check" alt="'ll check" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>check</i>) out around 6:30 tomorrow morning.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Will" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="need" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>need</i>) a taxi to the airport?
<b>B:</b>	Yes.
<b>A:</b>	Certainly.  We <blank word="will take" alt="'ll take" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>take</i>) care of that for you. Anything else?
<b>B:</b>	That’s all.  Thanks a lot.
<b>A:</b>	You’re welcome, Mr. Peterson.]]>
